    "The chatbot needs to generate new and contextually relevant answers for the users.",
    "The chatbot also needs to understand the cultural vocabulary of the users. 2.",
    "Determine the intellectual or proprietary data:The data for the graduate program is obtained from the program coordinator and the website, and it has been saved in a.txt file using key-value pairs.",
